quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  56,76,"Dájúdájú ìbúra ńlá ni, tí ẹ bá mọ̀."
  56,77,"Dájúdájú (al-Ƙur’ān) ni n̄ǹkan kíké alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé."
  56,78,"Ó wà nínú Tírà kan tí wọ́n ń fi ààbò bò (ìyẹn Laohul-Mahfūṭḥ)."
  67,16,"Ṣé ẹ fọkànbalẹ̀ sí Ẹni tí Ó wà ní (òkè) sánmọ̀ pé kò lè jẹ́ kí ilẹ̀ gbe yín mì? Nígbà náà, ilẹ̀ yó sì máa mì tìtì."
  67,17,"Tàbí ẹ̀ fọkànbalẹ̀ sí Ẹni tí Ó wà ní (òkè) sánmọ̀ pé kò lè fi òkúta iná ránṣẹ́ si yín ni? Nígbà náà, ẹ sì máa mọ bí ìkìlọ̀ Mi ti rí.{1}.",footnotes:1:[Ta ni Ẹni náà tí Ó wà ní òkè sánmọ̀ bí kò ṣe Allāhu - Ọba tó ga jùlọ -.]
  67,18,"Àwọn tó ṣíwájú wọn kúkú pe òdodo ní irọ́. Báwo sì ni bí Mo ṣe (fi ìyà) kọ (aburú fún wọn) ti rí!"
  68,10,"Má ṣe tẹ̀lé gbogbo ẹni tí ìbúra rẹ̀ pọ̀, ẹni yẹpẹrẹ,"
  68,11,"abúni, alárìnká tó ń sòfófó kiri,"
  68,12,"olùdènà iṣẹ́ rere, alákọyọ, ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀,"
  69,7,"Ó dẹ ẹ́ sí wọn fún òru méje àti ọ̀sán mẹ́jọ láì dáwọ́ dúró. O sì máa rí ìjọ náà tí wọ́n ti kú sínú rẹ̀ bí ẹni pé kùkùté igi dàbínù tó ti luhò nínú ni wọ́n.{1}.",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Fussilat; 41:16.]
  69,8,"Ǹjẹ́ o rí ẹnì kan nínú wọn tó ṣẹ́ kù bí?"
  69,9,"Fir‘aon àti àwọn tó ṣíwájú rẹ̀ àti àwọn ìlú tí wọ́n dojú rẹ̀ bolẹ̀ dé pẹ̀lú àwọn àṣìṣe."
  70,1,"Oníbèéèrè kan bèèrè nípa ìyà tó máa ṣẹlẹ̀"
  70,2,"sí àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́. Kò sì sí ẹni tí ó máa dí i lọ́wọ́"
  70,3,"lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu, Onípò-àyè gíga."